title: Stefon Diggs reflects on coming up short with Bills ahead of his first career Super Bowl with Patriots: 'Wish things were different'

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Stefon Diggs reflects on coming up short with Bills ahead of his first career Super Bowl with Patriots: 'Wish things were different'
sources.description: As he prepares to play in the Super Bowl for the rival Patriots, Stefon Diggs maintains his love for Josh Allen and the Buffalo Bills.
